snippet.title: Playthrough : Atari Jaguar - Supercross 3d
snippet.description: Released in december 1995, near the end of Jaguars lifespan. This motocross game could've been a great showdown of Jaguars power, but suffers from serious framerate issues (like 1-5 frames/ second all the time). It looks great in my opinion (but not in this video cause I basically messed everything up ripping), but doesnt offer too much variation. Everything looks the same, no matter which track. Btw this was my 2nd time playing this so thats why I suck and framerate makes this virtually unplayable. I don't recommend this at all unless it costs only a buck. P.s no 2 player mode. blah.
